12:08.858 --> 12:12.688
[walker growls]

12:16.387 --> 12:17.780
[Negan] It's not him.

12:30.445 --> 12:33.448
We'll wait here a beat so
the psycho won't sniff us out.

12:33.578 --> 12:35.493
Should give you enough time
to jack a car

12:35.624 --> 12:39.236
while Negan baits
the Croat down to the garage.

12:39.367 --> 12:41.151
You both hightail it
out of here,

12:41.282 --> 12:43.197
lure him halfway
across the city.

12:43.327 --> 12:44.633
Get him alone.

12:44.764 --> 12:46.287
That's when
we start skull-bashing

12:46.417 --> 12:48.332
and throat-cutting the Burazi.

12:49.943 --> 12:52.380
You get your kid.
We kill the psycho.

12:52.510 --> 12:54.295
Everybody wins a prize.

12:54.425 --> 12:56.471
How do we know if shit
goes sideways for you?

12:56.601 --> 12:57.864
You don't.

13:03.608 --> 13:05.393
Don't screw it up.

13:15.403 --> 13:16.796
Figured out how to bait him yet?

13:18.232 --> 13:20.887
Yeah, I got a thought or two.

13:21.017 --> 13:23.585
I feel good about this.

13:23.715 --> 13:26.283
It's gonna work, Maggie.

13:26.414 --> 13:28.111
We're gonna get your boy back.

13:31.723 --> 13:33.377
I have to tell you something.

13:40.341 --> 13:41.821
[door shuts]

13:53.397 --> 13:55.747
[Negan sighs]

13:57.532 --> 13:59.795
I can explain.

14:03.755 --> 14:06.454
You've done enough explaining.

14:06.584 --> 14:07.847
Don't act like
you've never did something

14:07.977 --> 14:11.111
you needed to explain.

14:11.241 --> 14:12.982
We don't have time for this.

14:26.866 --> 14:28.128
[whirring]

14:28.258 --> 14:30.695
[The Croat] [ speaking Croatian]
[chuckles]

14:33.655 --> 14:35.613
You understand
how to operate it?

14:38.834 --> 14:40.357
You sure?

14:45.406 --> 14:48.800
Eject the disc...

14:48.931 --> 14:51.064
and you press the button.

14:51.194 --> 14:52.543
Like so.

14:57.505 --> 14:59.115
You seem nervous.

15:01.639 --> 15:03.206
Are you afraid of me?

15:04.425 --> 15:06.514
No. Of course not.

15:06.644 --> 15:08.472
[The Croat] You are.

15:10.213 --> 15:12.737
You know, I still recall
the day you joined us.

15:13.564 --> 15:15.697
You were hiding
in a fire station

15:15.827 --> 15:18.830
with a group of barbarians.

15:18.961 --> 15:22.095
But you...

15:22.225 --> 15:25.533
you were smart.

15:25.663 --> 15:28.144
You laid down your weapon.

15:33.628 --> 15:39.112
It has been a joy
over these past few years

15:39.242 --> 15:43.072
watching you blossom into this

15:43.203 --> 15:48.251
strong, faithful...

15:48.382 --> 15:50.079
[speaking Croatian]

15:50.210 --> 15:53.517
confident protector.

15:54.823 --> 15:58.783
You have made me so proud.

16:00.002 --> 16:03.963
You should have no reason...

16:04.093 --> 16:07.444
to ever be afraid of me!

16:07.575 --> 16:09.055
Okay?

16:10.404 --> 16:13.581
[laughs] Okay.

16:25.245 --> 16:29.727
